U10 (74HCT245) : 
B0-B2 Sets SRAM Size
000 - 64KBit/8k
001 - 128KBit/16k
010 - 256KBit/32k
011 - 512KBit/64k - Official RAM Cart Size
100 - 1MBit/128k
101 - 2MBit/256k
110 - 4MBit/512k - Max Size (Schematic Reflects)~1~start~gge43361~0~pinpart
